name: Welcome to the Dark Clouds Minnesota United FC chants page
body:
As you can see there isn't anything here right now. Don't worry, I haven't scrapped the chants. I'm in the process of reworking the "under the hood" stuff for the site. I don't expect to have the site back up till February sometime. If you need the chants, give me a hollor on the /r/minnesotaunited sub on reddit.

-DrewOJensen
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
